{"tid":1510621,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葉劉：政府不應糾纏於追究任何人 特首應直接與群眾對話","createTime":"2019-08-27T09:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T01:50:37.000Z","uid":212626,"like":252,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"bec4191e11df39d55c0dc0e42f2ea3e54709edf2","tid":1510621,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:03:09.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員兼新民黨主席葉劉淑儀接受電台節目電話訪問時，回應有消息指政府考慮引用現行法例的《緊急情況規例條例》進行緊急立法，<span style=\"color: red;\">葉劉淑儀認為引用這條例有風險</span>，表示政府一直知道有相關權力，但問題在於會有甚麼效果，<span style=\"color: red;\">如有市民建議進行緊急立法禁制「蒙面」，但效果或令更多人「蒙面」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀認為，在今次事件結束後，政府不應糾纏於追究任何人，又相信行政長官林鄭月娥應直接與群眾對話。她指政府有最大誠意，但質疑民間的五大訴求很難做到，其中特赦無可能，因為會令刑事條例沒有阻嚇作用，又指成立獨立調查委員會並不適當。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e8%91%89%e5%8a%89%e6%b7%91%e5%84%80%ef%bc%9a%e5%bc%95%e7%94%a8%e3%80%8a%e7%b7%8a%e6%80%a5%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8b%e6%9c%89%e9%a2%a8%e9%9a%aa-186403\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e8%2591%2589%25e5%258a%2589%25e6%25b7%2591%25e5%2584%2580%25ef%25bc%259a%25e5%25bc%2595%25e7%2594%25a8%25e3%2580%258a%25e7%25b7%258a%25e6%2580%25a5%25e6%25b3%2595%25e3%2580%258b%25e6%259c%2589%25e9%25a2%25a8%25e9%259a%25aa-186403&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi5LurRSHZiEGX9rhKonVocs%3D&h=1c99697f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e8%91%89%e5%8a%89%e6%b7%91%e5%84%80%ef%bc%9a%e5%bc%95%e7%94%a8%e3%80%8a%e7%b7%8a%e6%80%a5%e6%b3%95%e3%80%8b%e6%9c%89%e9%a2%a8%e9%9a%aa-186403</a>"},{"pid":"f59d3e9a8d3176f2e99d3a9fa2a282dfad1c0dfc","tid":1510621,"uid":52817,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3badeb77c1f05cf1afb6516ffa884781a37a08d4","tid":1510621,"uid":33930,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"repl